<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23496669-queen-of-the-desert"><img alt="Queen of the Desert: A Biography of the Female Lawrence of Arabia, Gertrude Bell" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1434334443l/23496669._SX98_.jpg" />
